{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"WWDC16","title":"Validating HTTP Live Streams","role":"sampleCode","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Related Sessions","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Related-Sessions"},{"items":["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-504-Advances-in-HTTP-Live-Streaming","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC16-503-Advances-in-AVFoundation-Playback","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC16-504-Whats-New-in-HTTP-Live-Streaming"],"style":"list","type":"links"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"HTTP Live Streaming enables the reliable delivery of media content over a wide variety of network conditions. Learn best practices in HLS authoring, see how to verify your streams using the HTTP Live Streaming tools, and apply the results to improve the performance of your streams.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC16-510-Validating-HTTP-Live-Streams","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"kind":"article","sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/wwdc16\/510","isActive":true,"type":"reference","overridingTitle":"Watch Video (22 min)"}},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC16"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc16-510-validating-http-live-streams"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"references":{"https://developer.apple.com/wwdc16/510":{"url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/wwdc16\/510","checksum":null,"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/wwdc16\/510","type":"download"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC16-503-Advances-in-AVFoundation-Playback":{"abstract":[{"text":"AVFoundation is a powerful framework for media operations, providing capture, editing, playback, and export. Learn about new APIs and methods for media playback. Create seamless loops, simplify your playback logic with “autowait”, and see how to deliver an even faster playback startup experience.","type":"text"}],"role":"sampleCode","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc16-503-advances-in-avfoundation-playback","type":"topic","kind":"article","title":"Advances in AVFoundation Playback","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC16-503-Advances-in-AVFoundation-Playback"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC17-504-Advances-in-HTTP-Live-Streaming":{"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17-504-advances-in-http-live-streaming","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-504-Advances-in-HTTP-Live-Streaming","role":"sampleCode","kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"HTTP Live Streaming allows you to stream live and on-demand content to global audiences. Learn about great new features and enhancements to HTTP Live Streaming. Highlights include support for HEVC, playlist metavariables, IMSC1 subtitles, and synchronized playback of multiple streams. Discover how to simplify your FairPlay key handling with the new AVContentKeySession API, and take advantage of enhancements to offline HLS playback."}],"type":"topic","title":"Advances in HTTP Live Streaming"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes":{"images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"WWDCNotes.png"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"WWDC Notes","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes","abstract":[{"type":"t